---
import "../../styles/blog.css";
import Header from "../../components/header2.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/footer.astro";
import Footer2 from "../../components/footer2.astro";
import Sidebar from "../../components/Sidebar.astro";

import { Accordion, AccordionItem } from "accessible-astro-components";

const {
frontmatter: { title, description, pubDate, pubTime, image, author, credit },
} = Astro.props;
---

<html lang="en">
<Header />

<body>
  <div class="blog-container">
    <main>
      <a href="/blog/" class="back-button">Back to Blog</a>
      <article>
        <div class="article-head">
          <h1 class="title">{title}</h1>
          <small>Written by: {author}</small>
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="article-body">
          {image && <img width={720} height={360} src={image} alt="" />}
          <small>
            Published on: {pubTime} â€¢
            {pubDate && <time>{pubDate}</time>}
          </small>
          <small>
            {credit}
          </small>
          <hr />
          <slot />
        </div>
      </article>
      <br />
      <a href="/blog/" class="back-button">Back to Blog</a>
      <span>|</span>
      <a href="/" class="back-button">Back to Home</a>
    </main>
    <div class="sidebar-container">
      <Sidebar />
    </div>
  </div>
  <section>
    <div class="accordian-container">
      <Accordion>
        <AccordionItem header="Comprehensive Guides and Tutorials">
          <p>
            Welcome to our eBike website, where we strive to provide you with a wealth of information and resources to
            enhance your
            electric biking experience. Whether you're just starting out or have been riding for years, our
            comprehensive guides and
            tutorials are designed to be invaluable companions on your eBike adventures.
          </p>
          <br>
          <p>
            Our team of experts is passionate about electric biking and wants to share their knowledge with you. We
            understand that
            eBikes offer a unique and exciting way to explore the outdoors, commute to work, or simply enjoy a leisurely
            ride.
            That's why we've curated a collection of tips, tricks, and practical advice to help you make the most of
            your eBike.
          </p>
          <br>
          <p>
            For novice riders, we have beginner's guides that cover the basics of eBikes, including how they work,
            different types
            of eBikes available, and what to consider when purchasing your first one. We'll walk you through the process
            of
            understanding battery capacity, motor power, and other important specifications so you can make an informed
            decision.
            If you're already familiar with eBikes and looking to take your riding to the next level, our advanced
            guides and
            tutorials are here to help. We delve into topics such as maintenance and care, optimizing battery life, and
            improving
            performance. You'll learn how to properly clean and maintain your eBike, troubleshoot common issues, and
            ensure that
            your rides are as smooth and enjoyable as possible.
          </p>
          <br>
          <p>
            Safety is a top priority when it comes to eBiking, so we also provide comprehensive guides on riding
            etiquette, traffic
            laws, and gear recommendations. We want you to feel confident and secure while exploring the roads or trails
            on your
            eBike, and our safety tips will help you navigate any situation with ease.

            So, whether you're seeking advice on selecting the perfect eBike, learning how to maintain your current
            ride, or simply
            looking for inspiration and tips to elevate your eBike adventures, you've come to the right place. Explore
            our website,
            dive into our guides, and embark on an electrifying journey with your eBike. Tab to us and let's make your
            eBike
            experience unforgettable!
          </p>
          <br>
          <a href="" style="color: rgb(151, 151, 200)">coming soon</a>


        </AccordionItem>
        <AccordionItem header="Unbiased Reviews">
          <p>Transparency is a core value we uphold at EbikeOfficial. Our team of passionate reviewers conducts
            thorough
            tests on electric bikes, providing unbiased and detailed reviews. Our goal is to help you make an informed
            choice for
            your next ride with confidence.</p>
          <br>

          <p>Our dedicated team leaves no stone unturned when testing electric bikes. We evaluate various factors,
            including
            performance, design, battery life, motor power, and overall ride experience. By providing comprehensive and
            accurate
            information, we empower you to find the perfect eBike for your needs.</p>
          <br>
          <p>Independence and objectivity are the cornerstones of our reviews. We have no affiliations with specific
            eBike
            manufacturers, ensuring that our evaluations are unbiased. Our commitment is to equip you with knowledge and
            confidence, knowing that our reviews are based solely on the merits of each electric bike.</p>
          <br>
          <p>Investing in an electric bike is significant, and we want to be your trusted resource throughout the
            process. Our
            commitment to transparency and unbiased reviews ensures that you have the information you need to
            confidently select
            your next ride.</p>
          <br>
          <p>Join us at [Your eBike Website] to explore our comprehensive reviews and make your next eBike purchase with
            confidence. We are here to provide you with the best possible guidance as you embark on your electric biking
            journey.
          </p>
          <br>
          <a href="" style="color: rgb(151, 151, 200)">coming soon</a>

        </AccordionItem>
      </Accordion>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class=" footer-container">
    <!-- <Footer2 /> -->
    <Footer />
  </div>

  <style>
    .title {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin: 0.25em 0 0;
    }

    hr {
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    html {
      min-height: 100vh;
      height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      height: 100%;
      color: white;
      background: black;
    }

    .blog-container {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 3rem;
    }

    .accordian-container {
      margin: 3rem;
    }

    main {
      flex: 3;
    }

    .sidebar-container {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 0 0 0 2rem;
    }

    time {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .back-button {
      color: #818cf8;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      main {
        flex: 4;
      }

      .sidebar-container {
        display: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>

</html>